thread.title: Libyan Warlord Haftar Returns After Medical Treatment Abroad

author: Jared Malsin
title: Libyan Warlord Haftar Returns After Medical Treatment Abroad
text:
Libyan warlord Khalifa Haftar returned to Benghazi two weeks after he was hospitalized in Paris, appearing on local TV to end speculation about the health of one of the war-torn country’s most powerful leaders.
Mr. Haftar’s disappearance from the public eye fueled fears of a succession struggle that could have plunged Libya even deeper into crisis.
